{"tid":2377400,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"戒糖/戒甜討論，有冇同路人","createTime":"2021-01-23T14:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T11:41:37.000Z","uid":77320,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2fabfe9797318f1588ca2084aa87b73219db69e0","tid":2377400,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"因為皮膚問題已經戒食零食、朱古力、雪糕、甜品<br />\n啲人成日話食生果有益，但我連生果都戒埋<br />\n基本上淨係飲水，就算飲凍檸茶都係走甜<br />\n但感覺上都仲係未完全戒晒<br />\n另外因為成日食外賣<br />\n啱啱食咗個鰻魚飯（係，唔使旨意叫我戒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n一路食一路覺得好甜<br />\n後尾查返個鰻魚汁都落咗好多糖<br />\n點樣先確保完全戒晒糖<br />\n<br />\n唔想上網搵content farm文<br />\n係咪應該要搵專業營養師<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e26b303905bdd500cde6d7ee1b6c50283ad9a79","tid":2377400,"uid":22104,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"想戒但做唔到<br />\n最多持續到一個星期但感覺成個人都好虛弱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋越唔食越想食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7286e45e16f0b4ef70268a18edf32eac90b9462","tid":2377400,"uid":77320,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e26b303905bdd500cde6d7ee1b6c50283ad9a79","tid":2377400,"uid":22104,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"想戒但做唔到<br />\n最多持續到一個星期但感覺成個人都好虛弱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋越唔食越想食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"你係咪仲年紀細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n25歲打後口味會開始改變（包括對囡囡）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5681d49c0d743432b8077295083c860b7b8d10e","tid":2377400,"uid":22104,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7286e45e16f0b4ef70268a18edf32eac90b9462","tid":2377